<h2 id="adt">ADT</h2>
<h3 id="primitive-typesreference-types">Primitive Types/Reference Types</h3>
<ul>
  <li>primitive types
    <ul>
      <li>stack, exist only when in use</li>
      <li>immutable</li>
      <li>no ID, only value</li>
      <li>dirt cheap</li>
      <li>int, long, byte, short, char, float, double, boolean</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Object Reference Types
    <ul>
      <li>heap, garbage collected</li>
      <li>some mutable, some not</li>
      <li>ID + value</li>
      <li>more costly</li>
      <li>Classes, interfaces, arrays, enums, annotations</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="static-typesdynamic-types">Static Types/Dynamic Types</h3>
