  </li>
  <li>dynamic data types
    <ul>
      <li>åœ¨è¿è¡Œé˜¶æ®µè¿›è¡Œç±»å‹æ£€æŸ¥ â€“ value</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<h3 id="immutablemutable">Immutable/Mutable</h3>
<ul>
  <li>immutability - final
    <ul>
      <li>references / value cannot be changed</li>
      <li>final class cannot be inherited</li>
      <li>final method cannot be overridden by subclasses</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>String â€”â€” immutable</li>
  <li>StringBuilder â€”â€” mutable (never use Date)
    <ul>
      <li>é˜²å¾¡å¼æ‹·è´ defensive copy
